17:22.140 --> 17:23.539
Along with the myriad

17:23.570 --> 17:26.403
doomsday scenarios
that haunt ordinary preppers—-

17:26.440 --> 17:28.135
global pandemic,
nuclear holocaust,

17:28.180 --> 17:30.068
_socialist zombies
coming to eat their guns--

17:30.110 --> 17:32.704
the wealthy ones also worry
that the poor are gonna rise up

17:32.750 --> 17:34.479
